data.description: Welcome to 15 Whitts Forge lane, a beautiful 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home in Butler Station. The sellers have completed many updates including all new hardwood flooring on the main level and in the bathrooms, new carpeting in the stairwell, upstairs hallway and bedrooms. The entire house has been professionally painted including the trim and ceilings. Upon entering the home, to the right you are greeted with a large living room with a cozy gas fireplace. To the left, you are welcomed to the formal dining room area that could also be used as an office.The renovated kitchen has new cabinets, open shelves, butcher countertops, stainless steel appliances and a large bay window overlooking the backyard. The upstairs includes a large master suite, 2 additional bedrooms, and a secondary bath. The full baths have granite countertops, updated lighting and faucets. The half bath has a new mirror, vanity, and is located on the main level. The laundry room is also located on the main level. The backyard is nicely landscaped and includes a large deck.This elegant home has been completely renovated and is ready for a new family to enjoy nights by the gas fireplace, gatherings in the updated kitchen, and fun in the spacious backyard. Conveniently located; just a short distance from downtown Mauldin, shopping areas,15 minutes from downtown Greenville, accessible to major roads/highways, and highly rated schools.  Don't miss out on this great opportunity! Call us to arrange an appointment to view this well kept home.
